<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="image-n">image <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɪmɪdʒ/    美 /'ɪmɪdʒ/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>影像；图像；形象；印象：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He saw the image of his face in the mirror.
他在镜子里看到了自己的脸。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Littering makes our school dirty, and does harm to the <strong>image of</strong> our school.
乱扔垃圾使我们的学校脏乱，并且有损学校的形象。</p><footer>2011 浙江书面表达改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Interestingly, our self-images are often quite different from the images others hold about us.
有趣的是，我们的自我形象和别人对我们的印象往往大相径庭。</p><footer> 2008 广东</footer></div></div>